# Morning-scan output is NOT committed. These reports enumerate security
# findings (file:line) across many repos — publishing them in a public repo
# hands attackers a map of exploitable weaknesses. The CI workflow still
# uploads them as private GitHub Actions artifacts for history. Keep them local.
reports/
!reports/.gitkeep

